text:
[redacted_name]經過[redacted_name]在浴室門邊的他，走到窗台旁拉開窗簾，明亮的光線霎時充滿了臥室，前幾分鐘還充斥著的淫靡氣息瞬間消散。
「身高不是絕對。」
[redacted_name]在髮際比劃兩人身高的手被一把抓下，虎牙啃咬指尖，癢癢的帶點疼。
「是嗎。」
此時臉上的微笑，絕對不是因為自己知道了別人還不知道的他。
「你怎麼可以這麼閒？」
明明也算是小有名氣的模特兒，居然在自己家賴了兩天。
trans:
[redacted_name] passed [redacted_name] by the bathroom door, walked to the window and drew back the curtains. Bright light instantly filled the bedroom, and the lustful atmosphere that permeated the room just a few minutes ago dissipated right away.
"Height is not absolute."
[redacted_name]'s hand that was making a comparison of their heights was grabbed off her hairline, and her fingertips were chewed by his canine tooth, causing an itchy and a little painful sensation.
"Yes."
The smile on his face at this time was definitely not because she knew something about him that others didn't know yet.
"How can you have so much time?"
She is definitely a rather well-known model, but she actually stayed at his home for two days.
